      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh convergence study",
      "description": "Grid convergence index (GCI) computed for three mesh densities (coarse, medium, fine) at 3500 RPM / 6 LPM. Fine mesh selected for all subsequent simulations. GCI < 2% for velocity field; GCI < 5% for hemolysis index.",
      "outcome": "pass",
